[gd_scene load_steps=86 format=3]

; GRASS HUB — Grand Castle of the Penguin Realm
; Scale: player is ~1.5m tall. Castle footprint ~50x50m, ~25m tall,
;   with twin 28m spires. Terrain pad ~160x160m.
; Floors/rooms: front plaza, courtyard, entrance hall, east wing (mountain),
;   west wing (water), north wing (snow, 3*), south wing (lava, 5*),
;   upper landing, sand door (10*), sky door (15*), throne room,
;   bowser gate (25*), crypt basement, rooftop, reflecting pool,
;   dev-room attic, key rooms (3).
; Secrets: hidden-brick passage, crypt trapdoor, rooftop long-jump route,
;   reflecting-pool coins, three colored-key rooms, dev-room attic.
; Content: 4 bhvBobombBuddy, 4 bhvGoomba (plaza), 2 bhvGoomba (crypt),
;   3 bhvCuttlefish, 40+ coins_yellow, 8 coin_red, 3 stars (1 visible,
;   2 hidden), 4 oneup, 1 cap_wing, 1 cap_metal.
; Spawn: Vector3(0, 1.0, 16) facing -Z (castle lies northward).

